<L>__{exterior kigali airport tarmac. day}
<A>__{the van parked by the runway tarmac. african music plays on the radio. paul drums his fingers, checks his watch. zozo, porter driver, early thirties, sits nervously. an airport baggage handler approaches the van.}
<C>__{handler}
<D>__{sir, the flight is delayed one more hour.}
